    {
      "id": "result",
      "durationMs": 28500,
      "narration": {
        "text": "We did not write a physics engine, and that is the point: we took the industry standard. Box2D is Erin Catto's rigid-body engine, the one behind an entire generation of 2D hits, and JBox2D is its faithful Java port."
